{
  "texts": [
    "In light of this observation, a decision is made to refine the accuracy measurement approach to account for this characteristic behavior.",
    "The refined accuracy comprises the following steps:(1) Initially, the predicted classification labels for each set of 100 frames within a gesture are examined.",
    "It is essential to ensure that among these 100 frames, only one non-zero label is present.",
    "This criterion guarantees accurate prediction of the Background frames and ensures that each gesture is uniquely identified without any overlapping predictions with other gestures in the same frame sequence.",
    "(2) Subsequently, the correspondence between the ground truth non-zero labels and the non-zero predicted values within these 100 frames is validated."
  ]
}